data.description: Great investment opportunity or owner operator for this low maintenance duplex only a few blocks from Hinman park and the lake. These units were updated a few years ago with a new roof, new flooring, paint, granite countertops and a new deck. Each unit has 2 bedrooms and 1 full bath with gated and fully fenced yard. Each backyard has a storage shed. Long time tenant in place. This great property is ready for its new owner. 2023-10-20
